@say đắm
* verb
- to dote on

[say đắm] passionate; amorous 
 Nụ hôn say đắm 
 A passionate kiss 
 Yêu ai say đắm 
 To be deep/madly in love with somebody; 
 To be over head and ears in love with somebody; 
 To fall deeply in love with somebody; 
 To fall head over heels in love with somebody
